vote.title: A resolution (1) authorizing the ArtsActivate 2021 Program, a project-based cultural support program within the Office of Arts and Culture to support art and cultural services in the City of Dallas for FY 2020-21; and (2) approving the program guidelines - Financing: This action has no cost consideration to the City (see Fiscal Information)
